TableContextTimeStampBeforeTable: {9775=Krone North America presents the latest innovation in large square balers, the BiG Pack 1290 HDP II. This generation of large square balers from Krone increases the throughput by 50% more bales and the density by up to 10% more, when compared to the BiG Pack 1290 HDP. In order to achieve additional throughput and density the HDP II had many components upgraded, from the Active Pick-Up to the eight double knotters., 6597=10.23.2013}
